# sv-niteco-employees-sample
A portlet example of Niteco's employees management under Sitevision. This portlet has only a learning purpose.

## Dependencies
* SiteVision Server 3
* Maven

## Build and deployment
* In the root of the folder, run the command  `mvn clean install`
* Deploy manually to the server by copying the resulting file `/target/niteco-*.war` to `[Path to Sitevision server]/tomcat/webapps`

## Development
The project can be imported into Eclipse as a Java project.
